snippet.title: Raiden X - Longplay
snippet.description:
This game is a Raiden Fan Made based off Raiden II. I knew this game since 10 years ago. Before knew there is a official Raiden franchise just 3 years ago from Raiden Legacy and Raiden III. 

If you enjoyed this video you could play this game free at: http://www.raiden-x.net/
